        <type>size_t</type>
        <definition>size_t syn_stream_read_line</definition>
        <argsstring>(SYN_Stream *s, uint8_t *buf, size_t max_len)</argsstring>
        <name>syn_stream_read_line</name>
        <param>
          <type><ref refid="structSYN__Stream" kindref="compound">SYN_Stream</ref> *</type>
          <declname>s</declname>
        </param>
        <param>
          <type>uint8_t *</type>
          <declname>buf</declname>
        </param>
        <param>
          <type>size_t</type>
          <declname>max_len</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Read up to and including the next delimiter byte. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Reads bytes from the stream into <computeroutput>buf</computeroutput>, stopping after the first delimiter byte (which is included in the output). If no delimiter is found in the buffer, returns 0 and reads nothing.</para>
<para>Pair with PT_STREAM_WAIT in delimiter mode to wait for a complete line: <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">PT_STREAM_WAIT(pt,<sp/>&amp;stream);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">n<sp/>=<sp/>syn_stream_read_line(&amp;stream,<sp/>buf,<sp/>sizeof(buf));</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>s</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Stream instance. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>buf</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Destination buffer. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>max_len</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Maximum bytes to read (including delimiter). </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>Number of bytes read (0 if no delimiter found or empty). </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
